    <item>
      <title>丰田汽车产量因汽车安全丑闻和美国召回事件而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/toyota-production-falls-on-vehicle-safety-scandals-us-recalls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日本和中国市场的销量下滑终结了短暂的复苏势头，丰田汽车公司的销量再次下滑，而国内丑闻和海外召回事件又扰乱了生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/toyota-production-falls-on-vehicle-safety-scandals-us-recalls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
